title: Dinamo, Olympiacos upsetting the odds in Group F
text: Dinamo, Olympiacos upsetting the odds in Group F Friday, 9 October 2015 (2 minutes ago) Two surprise results have opened up Group F, and GNK Dynamo Zagreb and Olympiacos FC are both seeking a second win on matchday three.
